data.description: Nice 3 bedroom 1 bathroom home situated on a quiet secluded dead-end street in a great northeast Des Moines neighborhood. The primary bedroom features vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet plus a private door to the rear deck. All kitchen appliances plus stackable washer & dryer included. The oversized heated detached garage is a mechanic's dream! Featuring 10' side walls + a workshop with plenty of room for tools & storage, security system included. Extra long driveway with entry from front or private back alley. Property is adjacent to a city park with a paved walking trail. Located just northwest of the Iowa State Fairgrounds & close to library, aquatic center, shopping, and more. Easy access to I-235 and bus route for quick commutes. Being sold "as-is". All information obtained from Seller and public records.
